SQL_STMT_U.val: insert into werkbestand_saldi wb (wb.wb_relatie, wb.wb_rekening, wb.wb_rekening_soort, wb.wb_rekening_munt) ( select distinct ap.ap_relatienr, ap.ap_rekeningnr, ap.ap_rekening_soort, ap.ap_rekening_munts from aktuele_posities ap where ap.ap_relatienr between ~1 and ~2 and ((ap.ap_rekening_soort between 1000 and 1999 and ap.ap_saldo_positie < 0) or (ap.ap_rekening_soort between 100 and 999 and ap.ap_rekening_munts =' ' and ((ap.ap_optietype = ' ' and ap.ap_saldo_positie < 0) or (ap.ap_optietype = 'FUT' and ap.ap_saldo_positie <> 0) or ((ap.ap_optietype = 'CALL' or ap.ap_optietype = 'PUT') and (ap.ap_positie_long <> 0 or ap.ap_positie_short <> 0))))))
